name: Nabob
description: Nabob provides a decentralized financial asset which rewards users with a sustainable fixed compound interest model through use of it's unique Nab protocol. The Nabob Auto-Staking Protocol (Nab for short) is a new financial protocol that makes staking easier, more efficient and awards $Nabob token holders the highest stable returns in crypto. Nabob is a company focused on DeFi innovation that creates benefits and value for Nabob token holders.
